text: Pomarkku () is a municipality in Satakunta in Finland. It's nearby Pori and Kankaanpää. The municipality has a population of 2,196 (31 August 2017). In the civil war, Pomarkku had a big battle with several deads. == Other websites == * Municipality of Pomarkku – Official website Category:Municipalities of Satakunta
